Count} rows, {errors} errors, {warnings} warnings.</p>
      <ul>
        {issues.slice(0, 12).map((issue, index) => (
          <li key={`${issue.row}-${issue.field}-${index}`}>
            {issue.row ? `Row ${issue.row}: ` : ""}{issue.message}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  );
}
